{
  "texts": [
    "In-Depth Exploration:The formulation of research questions (RQ) addresses the holistic landscape of LIME and SHAP XAI frameworks for AD classification.",
    "The study conducts a thorough survey of these methods over the last decade, critically analysing their findings, results, capabilities, and limitations. 3.",
    "Practical Guidance: The study goes beyond theoretical analysis by providing Python-based code walkthroughs for implementing LIME and SHAP frameworks.",
    "This practical guidance is especially beneficial for newcomers entering the field, enhancing accessibility and application of the presented frameworks.The rest of the paper is structured as follows: Sect. 2 provides a brief overview of LIME and SHAP XAI frameworks.",
    "The search strategy is explained in Sect. 3."
  ]
}